title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2010-13 Ford Mustang Headlights
description:
This video offers a walkthrough of the installation process for removing and installing headlight assemblies on 2010-2012 Ford Mustang models. This video offers guidance for how to install three different versions of the headlight assembly: Crystal with LED Daytime Running Lights, Projector with LED Halo rings and LED Daytime Running Lights and Projector with CCFL Halo rings and LED daytime running lights. Regardless of which model you choose, each will give your Mustang a distinct, custom look with the clean lighting offered by LEDs or the crisp intensity of Cold Cathode Fluorescent Lighting

This video also demonstrates how to remove the front bumper of 2010-2012 Ford Mustang models for the DIY Enthusiast.
tags: Spyder Headlights, how to install spyder lights, Ford Mustang, Aftermarket headlights Mustang
